cc:Work.dc:title: Track map of the historical circuit Ain-Diab
cc:Work.dc:description: Created in Inkscape with data from Google Earth. Note: Google Earth shoswed me roads that were 50 years newer than last race at the track. Also, nothing remains of the paddocks remain other than empty ground. I made a guess as to the location of Pit Road based on the existing image and that empty ground.
